#DStv403 #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Search teams faced several challenges while looking for Khayalethu Magadla. Johannesburg Public Safety MMC David Tembe says robotics and the assistance of the police contributed to the recovery of the body. READ: Missing Soweto boy's body found Magadla fell into a manhole in Soweto while playing with friends three weeks ago. His body was found by search teams on Saturday. 